You can click on the signal to change its state.
You have unlimited undo/redo capabilities.
You can click on the bullet on the left to select a signal.
You can move the bullet on the left to move the trace horizontally.
You can right-click on the bullets on the left to delete a trace.
You can add an clock/signal/bus through menu: Edit->Add... .
You can add/remove time compressors with the triangle-tool by clicking on the bottom axis.
You can change the distance at the top/bottom of a signal when it is active.
You can activate a signal by clicking on the bullet on the left.
You can add vertical lines with the ruler-tool.
You can edit text with the I-beam-tool.
You can "File->Export to SVG" to export a vector graphic of the diagram for your documentation.
